    "#### The AnomalySineGenerator provides synthetic time-series data with injected anomalies, ideal for testing anomaly detection models. Key benefits include:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Controlled Anomaly Injection: You can control the anomaly percentage, allowing for clear evaluation of detection algorithms.\n",
    "2. Sine Wave with Noise: Simulates real-world cyclical data, like sensor readings, with added noise for realistic testing.\n",
    "3. Versatility: The data can be used for streaming anomaly detection models, offering flexibility in adjusting parameters.\n",
    "4. Balanced Evaluation: Visual comparison between normal data and anomalies helps assess model performance.\n",
    "5. Customizability: Allows adjustments to sample size, noise levels, and anomaly rates for targeted testing."
